cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.SY 

The paper proposes a new algorithm based on the GAIL framework for solving practical MDP problems with low-level and high-dimensional state input, such as image sequences. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), robotics (cs.RO), and systems and control (cs.SY). The focus on image sequences and the use of a global encoder also suggest a strong possibility for cs.CV.
